        {# update info #}
        <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading pointer collapsed js-more-info" id="update-account" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#detail-update-account">
                    <span class="pull-right" id="arrow-down-update-account">{{ icon('chevron-down') }}</span>
                    <span class="pull-right" id="arrow-up-update-account" style="display: none;">{{ icon('chevron-up') }}</span>
                    How can I update my information?
                </div>
                <div id="detail-update-account" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        First login to your CAIF account. If you don't remember your password, see <a class="js-more-info" id="issue-login" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#detail-issue-login">I can't login to my account</a>. Once you have logged in, click the link "Edit Profile" in your profile.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
    </div>
